  <entry>
    <title>Hexo博客快速写作与发布指南</title>
    <link href="https://zhulaoqi.github.io/2026/03/19/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/"/>
    <id>https://zhulaoqi.github.io/2026/03/19/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</id>
    <published>2026-03-19T04:30:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2026-03-19T03:45:27.494Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这是一份写给自己的备忘录：如何在这个 Hexo + NexT 博客中用最短路径完成”写文章 → 本地预览 → 发布上线”的全流程。</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="一、30-秒发布一篇文章"><a href="#一、30-秒发布一篇文章" class="headerlink" title="一、30 秒发布一篇文章"></a>一、30 秒发布一篇文章</h1><p>最快的路径，只需要三条命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1. 新建文章（自动生成 md 文件和 front-matter）</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo new <span class="string">&quot;你的文章标题&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2. 用你喜欢的编辑器写文章</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 文件在 source/_posts/你的文章标题.md</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 3. 一键部署上线</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo clean &amp;&amp; npx hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>没了。等 1-2 分钟 GitHub Pages 缓存刷新，线上就能看到。</p><h1 id="二、文章模板（Front-matter）"><a href="#二、文章模板（Front-matter）" class="headerlink" title="二、文章模板（Front-matter）"></a>二、文章模板（Front-matter）</h1><p>每篇文章头部的 YAML 配置决定了文章的元信息：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">文章标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">Kinch.zhu</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2026-03-19 12:00:00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">标签1</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">标签2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">分类名</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">这里是文章正文...</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;!--</span> <span class="string">more</span> <span class="string">--&gt;</span>   <span class="string">←</span> <span class="string">这行以上的内容会显示在首页作为摘要</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>常用分类参考：</strong></p><ul><li><code>技术思考</code> — 架构设计、技术趋势分析</li><li><code>设计文档</code> — 技术方案、系统设计</li><li><code>实用指南</code> — 教程、备忘录</li><li><code>踩坑记录</code> — Bug 修复、问题排查</li></ul><h1 id="三、完整工作流"><a href="#三、完整工作流" class="headerlink" title="三、完整工作流"></a>三、完整工作流</h1><h2 id="3-1-写作阶段"><a href="#3-1-写作阶段" class="headerlink" title="3.1 写作阶段"></a>3.1 写作阶段</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 新建文章</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo new <span class="string">&quot;文章标题&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 新建草稿（不会发布，适合未完成的文章）</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo new draft <span class="string">&quot;草稿标题&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 草稿写完后发布（从 _drafts 移到 _posts）</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo publish <span class="string">&quot;草稿标题&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-2-本地预览"><a href="#3-2-本地预览" class="headerlink" title="3.2 本地预览"></a>3.2 本地预览</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 启动本地服务器（支持热重载，改完文件刷新即可）</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo server</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 浏览器打开 http://localhost:4000</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 写完后 Ctrl+C 停止</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-3-部署上线"><a href="#3-3-部署上线" class="headerlink" title="3.3 部署上线"></a>3.3 部署上线</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 清理 + 部署（推荐每次都 clean）</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo clean &amp;&amp; npx hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果只想生成静态文件但不部署</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-4-一条龙命令"><a href="#3-4-一条龙命令" class="headerlink" title="3.4 一条龙命令"></a>3.4 一条龙命令</h2><p>把预览和部署合成一条：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 预览满意后直接部署</span></span><br><span class="line">npx hexo clean &amp;&amp; npx hexo generate &amp;&amp; npx hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="四、Markdown-写作技巧"><a href="#四、Markdown-写作技巧" class="headerlink" title="四、Markdown 写作技巧"></a>四、Markdown 写作技巧</h1><h2 id="4-1-图片管理"><a href="#4-1-图片管理" class="headerlink" title="4.1 图片管理"></a>4.1 图片管理</h2><p>推荐两种方式：</p><p><strong>方式一：放在 source&#x2F;images&#x2F; 目录</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">图片描述</span>](<span class="link">/images/my-image.png</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>方式二：使用图床（推荐）</strong><br>使用 PicGo 等工具上传到 GitHub&#x2F;OSS 图床，获取外链直接引用。避免仓库体积膨胀。</p><blockquote><p>⚠️ 不要使用 Typora 的本地绝对路径（如 <code>/Users/xxx/Library/...</code>），部署后图片会 404。</p></blockquote><h2 id="4-2-代码块"><a href="#4-2-代码块" class="headerlink" title="4.2 代码块"></a>4.2 代码块</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">```javascript</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">const hello = &quot;world&quot;;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>支持的语言高亮：<code>javascript</code>、<code>python</code>、<code>bash</code>、<code>java</code>、<code>sql</code>、<code>yaml</code>、<code>json</code> 等。</p><h2 id="4-3-表格"><a href="#4-3-表格" class="headerlink" title="4.3 表格"></a>4.3 表格</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| 列1 | 列2 | 列3 |</span><br><span class="line">|-----|-----|-----|</span><br><span class="line">| A   | B   | C   |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-4-数学公式"><a href="#4-4-数学公式" class="headerlink" title="4.4 数学公式"></a>4.4 数学公式</h2><p>本博客已配置 MathJax，直接使用 LaTeX 语法：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">行内公式：$E = mc^2$</span><br><span class="line">独立公式：$$\sum<span class="emphasis">_&#123;i=1&#125;^&#123;n&#125; x_</span>i$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="五、项目结构速查"><a href="#五、项目结构速查" class="headerlink" title="五、项目结构速查"></a>五、项目结构速查</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">githubBlog/</span><br><span class="line">├── _config.yml              # Hexo 主配置（站点信息、部署配置）</span><br><span class="line">├── themes/next/_config.yml  # NexT 主题配置（样式、功能开关）</span><br><span class="line">├── source/</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── _posts/              # ✏️ 文章放这里</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── _drafts/             # 📝 草稿放这里</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── _data/               # 🎨 自定义样式/模板</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── images/              # 🖼️ 图片资源</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── about/               # 关于页</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── tags/                # 标签页</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── categories/          # 分类页</span><br><span class="line">│   └── schedule/            # 日程页</span><br><span class="line">├── scaffolds/               # 文章模板</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── post.md              # hexo new 用的模板</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── draft.md             # hexo new draft 用的模板</span><br><span class="line">│   └── page.md              # hexo new page 用的模板</span><br><span class="line">└── public/                  # 生成的静态文件（不要手动改）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="六、常见问题"><a href="#六、常见问题" class="headerlink" title="六、常见问题"></a>六、常见问题</h1><p><strong>Q: 部署后线上没更新？</strong><br>A: 检查两件事：① <code>_config.yml</code> 的 <code>deploy.branch</code> 是否与 GitHub 仓库默认分支一致；② GitHub Pages 有 1-2 分钟缓存，等一等或强制刷新（Ctrl+Shift+R）。</p><p><strong>Q: 本地预览正常但部署后样式丢失？</strong><br>A: 检查 <code>_config.yml</code> 中的 <code>url</code> 和 <code>root</code> 是否正确配置了你的 GitHub Pages 地址。</p><p><strong>Q: 怎么删除一篇文章？</strong><br>A: 直接删除 <code>source/_posts/</code> 下对应的 <code>.md</code> 文件，然后重新部署。</p><p><strong>Q: 想改博客样式？</strong><br>A: 编辑 <code>source/_data/styles.styl</code>，不要直接改 <code>themes/next/</code> 里的文件。</p><hr><p><em>保持写作，保持输出。最好的笔记系统是你真正在用的那一个。</em></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;这是一份写给自己的备忘录：如何在这个 Hexo + NexT 博客中用最短路径完成”写文章 → 本地预览 → 发布上线”的全流程。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
